title: Omega Squad Teemos VO changed
body: Omega squad teemo's vo changed to his classic voice. It only changes back when he attacks, uses his w and ulting.

replies.body:
Hey StormStrike1 -

Thanks for the report! We are aware of issues where skins that have different VO than the base are having issues playing the proper VO. We're in the process of working on a fix. ^-^
